<br />\n風雨蘭熱線：2375 5322<br />\n撒瑪利亞防止自殺會：2389 2222<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">現階段不適合起強姦犯底，因為有機會影響法律程序。 </span><br />\n外傳：有幾條仆街喺原post不停口賤二度傷害該絲打。歡迎各位自行了斷啲賤人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">賤人list: </span><br />\n柯屎。魔鬼 <br />\n<br />\n原post: 『比人老強，可以點做』<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/39504/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/39504/page/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n跟進post(1)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/39715/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/39715/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"4d54f52ea67813a5bb40b2ecf2bdb9cd08766ffe","tid":40281,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:46:19.000Z","msg":"而家呢個Post變為支持事主既Post, 讓事主感受到連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ec3050c3257f6bfdb34f6cf9fb68ffef396e85","tid":40281,"uid":35308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:48:26.000Z","msg":"警訊話吾好冲凉保持犯罪證據, 吾好冲凉呀親"},{"pid":"0084aceeaf4ad10fb91d921058e247ae637e7818","tid":40281,"uid":11461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:49:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0303bde348bac8de51950f404f697bbfa53847c6","tid":40281,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:09:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警訊話吾好冲凉保持犯罪證據, 吾好冲凉呀親</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吾你老母<br />\n親你老母<br />\n<br />\n報左警親有警察帶佢去法醫度拿精液樣本架啦，<br />\n你人蠢就死撚左佢算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72892d740396815f254856762f03796c1325f1ca","tid":40281,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:10:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警訊話吾好冲凉保持犯罪證據, 吾好冲凉呀親</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n( Show Blocked User - 殺你呀媽 )"},{"pid":"9fc3bec8df2aab06049f0397c9e69d44350c249b","tid":40281,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:10:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><b